Corporate Outline
Our headquarters is located in Tokyo; our staff are located across the world dedicated to the institutional and retail investment management businesses.
More info



Number of employees:
data as of March 31, 2017

1345






Corporate History
We were originally formed in 1959 as Nomura Securities Investment Trust Management Co., Ltd. (NSITM), specializing in Japanese investment trust fund management. 
In 1981 Nomura Investment Management Co., Ltd. (NIMCO) was established to provide segregated investment services to institutional investors. In 1997, following a merger between NIMCO and NSITM, Nomura Asset Management was formed.
More info



