Overview


BuyerZone.com, LLC is an e-market place for business to business purchasing. The company offers procurement advice and a free request for quote tool set for 100 types of business purchases including office equipment , HR services, office furniture, internet services, telecommunications equipment, marketing services and retail products and services. 


